Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:03.78,DogDays-narrator,cou,0000,0000,0000,,The one-on-one fights that took \Nplace in the sky and on land:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:05.87,DogDays-narrator,rico,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-sama and the chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:08.75,DogDays-narrator,rico,0000,0000,0000,,and the serious battle between \Nthe Princess and Rebecca-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.53,DogDays-narrator,cou,0000,0000,0000,,There were countless exciting things,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:13.10,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,like plenty of fanshots,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.69,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,the appearance of Hero Mask, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:17.16,DogDays-narrator,cou,0000,0000,0000,,So what was the result after that kind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.76,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,of opening day of Union Fest?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:59.64,DogDays-ep-title,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)\an7}Change My Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:59.64,DogDays-narrator,ann1,0000,0000,0000,,The opening battle of \Nthe Union Fest is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.86,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,We will now announce the \Nbattle results on the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:04.22,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite unexpected,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.73,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Principality of \NPastillage is in first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.39,DogDays-main,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,They were slightly behind \Nin the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.39,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but started to catch up at an \Nincredible pace in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.85,DogDays-main,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, they pulled \Nthrough and caused an upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:15.94,DogDays-main,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Couverte-sama, what would you say \Nlead to your victory this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:20.00,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course all of our \Npeople did their very best,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.70,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it might have been \Nthat person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:28.50,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,People of Pastillage, \NI am here to aid you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.25,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the undefeatable Hero Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.06,DogDays-main,sin,0000,0000,0000,,Did Adel-sama stop caring \Nabout hiding her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:36.21,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's really let herself go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.82,DogDays-main,leo,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:40.35,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you'll have to face me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:41.30,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.50,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, Leonmichelli and Nanami,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:45.93,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will meet you in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.05,DogDays-main,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,She's really popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:51.19,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage's savior, Hero Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.06,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The spectators already love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.40,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all do our best again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.10,DogDays-main,ann,0000,0000,0000,,The second day will be a sea battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.25,DogDays-main,ann,0000,0000,0000,,All the contestants for \Nthe various beach events
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.21,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,have already gathered here \Non this beach battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.36,DogDays-main,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,The intra-country friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.79,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,marine race will be held here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.78,DogDays-main,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Also, on the field specially \Nset up for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.15,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Princess' project
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:26.22,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mounted Battle by the \NSea - Water battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.20,DogDays-main,ann,0000,0000,0000,,is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.48,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Let the water battle by the sea begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:41.04,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,The sky we both
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:44.74,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,gazed up at on that day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.74,DogDays-main,leo,0000,0000,0000,,Galette army! Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.14,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.49,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,I love these events!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.54,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's just keep our \Nlead all the way to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.76,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing that we could all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.37,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.12,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:04:00.04,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,run together someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.38,DogDays-main,yuk,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go in as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:03.76,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "Goodbye",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.58,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,it's "we will meet again."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:11.64,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know my wish will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:18.52,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's embrace our passionate memories
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:22.87,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,of those days that we rushed through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:29.08,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,That promise we made \Nhand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:35.03,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,We will meet again and it'll come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.92,DogDays-narrator,nana,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, the second \Nday of Union Fest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.67,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,was another huge success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:40.78,DogDays-song,song,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.90,DogDays-narrator,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, there were many
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.08,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,more events after that and Rico-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:43.30,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and Noir-chan even scored \Nbig at a quiz competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.69,DogDays-main,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Chief Ricotta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.05,DogDays-main,rico,0000,0000,0000,,General Godwin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.01,DogDays-main,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:54.06,DogDays-narrator,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Knights and common \Nfolk mingled on stage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.80,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and everybody had fun together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.88,DogDays-main,god,0000,0000,0000,,Next, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.96,DogDays-narrator,nana,0000,0000,0000,,The level of excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.82,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,stayed high during the \Nrest of the events...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:20.35,DogDays-main,rola,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, all the \Nwar games between our
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:22.34,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,three countries have been concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.41,DogDays-main,ban,0000,0000,0000,,The sporting \Nand art events
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.39,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,are still going on and there's \Nalso the final stage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.56,DogDays-main,ban,0000,0000,0000,,that'll take place on the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.60,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, for now, we've \Nconcluded this section.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:36.21,DogDays-main,rola,0000,0000,0000,,There were no major accidents \Nor other trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.39,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,during the large scale \Nevents, which is all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.50,DogDays-main,rola,0000,0000,0000,,thanks to your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:44.60,DogDays-main,ban,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear a toast \Nfrom the representative
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.73,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of the three countries' \Nknight orders, Lord Risler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.86,DogDays-main,cara,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.37,DogDays-main,rola,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.87,DogDays-main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Risler!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:56.37,DogDays-main,cara,0000,0000,0000,,Um, then I'd like to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.48,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,toast to the continued peace, \Nprosperity, and even better
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.42,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,cooperation between the three countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:02.68,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:04.94,DogDays-main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:05.71,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.92,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:10.35,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Becky, Cou-sama. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.75,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, you're going on a walk with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.26,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Princess again \Ntomorrow morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:17.27,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she said there's a \Nplace she wanted to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.71,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.65,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Cou-sama, Rebecca-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:23.09,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.40,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Millihi-nee, perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.40,DogDays-main,Mil,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.42,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,You're have your on-air performance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.17,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in our country tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:34.53,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca and I wanted to bring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.37,DogDays-main,milL,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:38.87,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Where will you be going \Nfor your walk tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.71,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.28,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go to a place
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.92,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with many memories that \Nwe haven't been to lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:03.30,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to this \Nstream in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.69,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, you had your training \Ncamp here last time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.90,DogDays-main,sin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, with Yukki, Ecle, and Noir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.45,DogDays-main,yuk,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.82,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.46,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for wanting \Nto come over so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.93,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.96,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you're always more than welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:29.01,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Are Lady d'Arquien and \NIsuka-san in today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.88,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,They left early in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:35.10,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to get some metal for his swordsmithing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.60,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:40.04,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones at our house \Nare Kanata and myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.44,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so please stay as long as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.62,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.75,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.87,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze's tail pillow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.68,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as fluffy and \Nsoft as I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.31,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, want to try it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.55,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,It's really fluffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:15.14,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I guess I'll try later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.63,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.76,DogDays-main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.77,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,You two really get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:26.29,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,She played with me a lot \Nwhen I was smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:30.19,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No no, you were the one \Nwho took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:34.99,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,When you were young,\N I was a tiny thing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.82,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.08,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kanata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:42.00,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.99,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect that it's thanks \Nto the Princess and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.72,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ecle and the others that Yuki-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:47.96,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,grew into what she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:51.47,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Normally local gods grow \Nbigger when their god rank
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:55.34,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,goes up after they've done\Nenough virtuous deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.42,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,From the time the lady picked me up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:01.85,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,until very recently,\N I was always a tiny thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.55,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,There was even a time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.68,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when you were smaller \Nthan Ecle or myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:09.41,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I guess seeing \Nyou get bigger each day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:13.22,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,made me want to be bigger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.61,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I trained really hard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.74,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,and when I realized what had happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:21.04,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:24.32,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to keep her clothed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.62,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because she grew so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:31.13,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But I really think I won't \Nget any taller than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.27,DogDays-main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.48,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.41,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:56.24,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just saw something \Non the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.33,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,See, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.63,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,A jewel? Or egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:05.33,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.33,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Does it belong to \NIsuka-san or Adel-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.12,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! Yuki-chan! Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.85,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,An... animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.69,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,A local god?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.28,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.28,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:43.92,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:44.88,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.98,DogDays-main,kaan,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, I didn't mean you, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:51.35,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.53,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:04.97,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.75,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yukki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:14.58,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,I am over there, this is \Nthe Princess' body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.57,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sink...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.32,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,And the Princess is me, Yukikaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.89,DogDays-main,all,0000,0000,0000,,We got switched around...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.21,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.61,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:38.24,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Th-then who's inside the \NHero who just left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.92,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Probably what was in this \Nlittle thing before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.07,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to catch it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.36,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call for help! Brave Connect On!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.44,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.71,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,I see, it makes sense that our moves
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.86,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,won't work with a different body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.07,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, we'll have to \Nchase the escaped Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.70,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Princes- I mean Yukki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:09.69,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't run around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.71,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my clothes- whoa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.21,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,My legs won't move like \NI want them to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:18.86,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Princ- Yukki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:19.96,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,...move...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.57,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.31,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I will hurry and find myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:36.47,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yukki, you keep the \NPrincess' body safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.86,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:42.62,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to treat \NYukki's body carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:49.91,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,But still, we can't just \Nleave it all to Sink alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:53.08,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry Prince- Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.84,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret Squad's \Nalready on the hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.18,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I jumped too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.99,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have to remember how \NYukki runs and moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.69,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sign to meet up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.50,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, Yukki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.46,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.85,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,We found out where your body is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:21.77,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:25.55,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's through the eastern path, \Nby the the old pine tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.56,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret Squad's got it surrounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.10,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but then it climbed up the tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.20,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work Secret Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.23,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can catch it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:36.64,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:39.40,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let's catch it with teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:40.39,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:00.17,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Style Ninja Art \N- Lightning Blossom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.61,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.31,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.49,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.90,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Prince- Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.01,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:58.60,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Braze Drive - Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.29,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Justice is served!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:21.66,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, Yukki, Kanata-san. \NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.95,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.92,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.06,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's happening again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.98,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.44,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still Sink in Yukki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:48.45,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Millihiore. I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.62,DogDays-main,sin,0000,0000,0000,,Inside Sink is me indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.42,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.93,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The monster and the Princess are back in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.93,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,their own bodies while Yukki \Nand myself are switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:07.28,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,That's all thanks to \Nyour quick judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.34,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.28,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been \Nnice if you two could
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.81,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,have returned to normal as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.28,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered that Sink was holding
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:21.21,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that jewel when we first got switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:24.23,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought that this little guy maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.40,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,switches bodies with \Nthe one closest to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:28.21,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,And when that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.65,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,those who are close to \Nit also get switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.99,DogDays-main,sinK,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:35.94,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad that at least the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.95,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess was able to get her body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.32,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Let's quickly find a way to get Sink and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.80,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.45,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.96,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yukki, can you try using \Nthe Brave Connect?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.71,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.96,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Brave Connect On!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.00,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.25,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that thing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:01.71,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,That little one isn't a \Nmonster, but a sprite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:06.18,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,I took it there to set it \Nfree far from civilization, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:09.81,DogDays-main,val,0000,0000,0000,,But last night you got too \Nexcited and forgot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:12.32,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,How do we get back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.27,DogDays-main,val,0000,0000,0000,,You should return to normal \Nwithout having to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:17.37,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but we're on our way there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.57,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go there at supersonic speeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:24.83,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.93,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.58,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,We'll arrive at the \NFuugetsu Lodge soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.82,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have to explain this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:33.84,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.57,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Your bodies got switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.91,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right now I am Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.59,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,And I am Yukikaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.64,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,A body switching sprite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.97,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.79,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,With this thing the fun possibilities \Nare nearly endless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.35,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Cou-sama! This is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.18,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.30,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,We have to return it to Adel-sama. So no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.45,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, Yukikaze, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:07.48,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,This all happened because \NI found that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.25,DogDays-main,both,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:12.27,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing for you to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.30,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to resolve it \Nthrough our teamwork anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:19.96,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,This will be just another \Nfun memory from the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:20.80,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:24.13,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Right, then we'll be \Ntaking Millihi-nee with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.12,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,See you two later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.81,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Call us on the Brave Connect \Nif anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.26,DogDays-main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:31.58,DogDays-main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:43.65,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Let's relax a bit until \NAdel-sama arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:44.28,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:47.27,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,But since we got dirty during the fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.31,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,how about a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.06,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.69,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, right now's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.69,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't see any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.26,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are we back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.88,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:05.16,DogDays-overlap,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.78,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,My own body \Nfits me the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:08.59,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:10.31,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,It just feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.52,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.01,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I really have to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:22.85,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,for treating my body with such care
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:25.03,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when we were switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.20,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I didn't fall \Ndown or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.70,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You looked cool in action, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:33.69,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it's easy \Nto move in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:36.43,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If I try hard enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:39.34,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can reproduce \Nthe "Body Switching" move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:42.61,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,How about we try switching \N bodies and not telling anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.05,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.18,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:54.19,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,It's good Sink and Yuki-chan \Nwere able to return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.72,DogDays-main,mill,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:57.14,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Heroes have arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:00.79,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't had a shortage of fun events.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:02.37,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,And lots of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.66,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's all fun, it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.52,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,For me there've been a lot of firsts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:10.66,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a wonderful summer \Nwith plenty of great memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:18.89,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,The Union Fest kind \Nof went by in a blur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:22.40,DogDays-main,leo,0000,0000,0000,,The time for you Heroes to \Nreturn is drawing closer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.09,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.67,DogDays-main,leo,0000,0000,0000,,When you have days off over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:28.39,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you're always welcome to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.64,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:33.18,DogDays-main,leo,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we'll have to summon\N you at a more relaxing time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.31,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so you won't have as\N much work as this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:39.44,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! I love the Hero work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:42.36,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I'd like to go out with
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.01,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the three rulers and the three Heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.65,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,before we go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:49.42,DogDays-main,leo,0000,0000,0000,,True, at Pastillage that \Ndidn't really work out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.33,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because of the trouble \Nwith the demon king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:55.16,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a nice summer \Nmemory of just being lazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:33.63,DogDays-main,adel,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I got too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:35.39,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've sealed away that mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:25:00.00,DogDays-next-ep-title,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1)}Final Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:38.15,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me show you my \NNinja Art - Body Switching!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:39.74,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing that!
